        ss.AvgScrRead,

        schools s

FROM 
    RankedSchools

    T1.Segment,
    T2.Consumption,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY T1.Segment ORDER BY T2.Consumption ASC) AS rn
  FROM 
    customers AS T1

  CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN Segment = 'KAM' THEN Consumption ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) / COUNT(CASE WHEN Segment = 'KAM' THEN Consumption END) AS LAM_KAM,

  CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN Segment = 'SME' THEN Consumption ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) / COUNT(CASE WHEN Segment = 'SME' THEN Consumption END) AS KAM_SME
FROM 
  RankedConsumption

  rn = 1;

    yearmonth y12
  JOIN 
    yearmonth y13
  ON 
    y12.CustomerID = y13.CustomerID
  JOIN 
    customers c
  ON 
    y12.CustomerID = c.CustomerID
  WHERE 
    y12.`Date` LIKE '2012%' 
    AND y13.`Date` LIKE '2013%' 
    AND c.Currency = 'EUR'
)
